resources.string:
AppointClinic is an app which allows patients to quickly and simply keep track of their health by easily accessing the clinics.
The means of access could be chatting as well as calling.
You can also search for reliable, research-backed answers to your questions about diseases, symptoms and health procedures. Plus, you can easily request an appointment with world-class experts in top-ranked specialties.

Note:- *Re-login if app crashes*
